Main components
- rankserver: web server (listens on http/4001, https/4002 by default)
- dfticker: periodic data fetcher
- twitter_ticker: periodic twitter poster

Dependency
- make
- Go
- Perl
- msgpack:      "https://github.com/ugorji/go/codec"
- lz4:          "https://github.com/bkaradzic/go-lz4"
- sqlite3:      "https://github.com/mattn/go-sqlite3"
- yaml:         "https://gopkg.in/yaml.v2"
- Net::Twitter: "https://metacpan.org/release/Net-Twitter"
- [optional] gopacket: "https://github.com/google/gopacket"

Embedded libraries
- rijndael: from "https://github.com/agl/pond.git"
- stoppableListener: from "https://github.com/hydrogen18/stoppableListener"
- jquery and jquery mobile
- date.js

External web dependencies
- Google charts: "https://developers.google.com/chart/"

To run a full service
- write config files
- make fetch
- make server
- make twitter

